title: High school Volleyball | Thursday’s results
text:
Published: Sat, October 17, 2015 @ 12:00 a.m. 
Columbiana 24-25-25-21-15SFlbLeetonia 26-11-13-25-12 
For Columbiana (9-13), Dee Dixon had 16 kills, Morgan Highley had 11 points, Haley Tohm had four blocks, Emily Gosselin had 22 assists and 12 points, and Hannah Hum had 47 digs. For Leetonia (4-17), Ariel Smith had 26 assists, Aurora Smith had 12 kills, Kristy Eckman had three blocks, and Caitlin Lewis had 27 digs. JV: Columbiana 2, Valley Christian 0. 
East Palestine 25-14-25-25 Wellsville 22-25-12-12 
For East Palestine, Jessica Leake had 19 kills and three blocks, Brysten Trosky had 12 points, and Marlaina Frye had 23 assists. For Wellsville, Kiki Perry had 10 blocks, Ashley Bennett had 15 kills, and Regan Pierson had 38 assists.
